              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3932631-robin-lee-hatcher?shelf=audiobooks">audiobooks</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/3932631-robin-lee-hatcher?shelf=2021-challenge">2021-challenge</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3733228274" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4019362911426259345">How fun to return to this classic children&apos;s story! Written at the end of the 1800&apos;s, it still holds all of its charm and truth.</span>
  <span id="freeText4019362911426259345" style="display:none">How fun to return to this classic children's story! Written at the end of the 1800's, it still holds all of its charm and truth.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4019362911426259345" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
